No. A-02-108: State v. Roundtree. Appeal dismissed. See, rule 7A(2); Neb. Rev. Stat. ยง 25-1301 (Cum. Supp. 2000).

No. A-02-113: State v. Poisel. Motion of appellant to dismiss appeal sustained; appeal dismissed.

No. A-02-125: State v. Stovall. Motion of appellee for summary affirmance sustained; judgment affirmed. See rule 7B(2).
No. A-02-126: Witmer v. Ashcroft. Pursuant to appellant's motion to dismiss, appeal dismissed.
No. A-02-127: Denison v. Pfizer Animal Health. Stipulation allowed; appeal dismissed.
